    button.modal-close(data-izimodal-close="")
      img(src="img/modals/modal-close-icon.svg", alt="Close")
    .modal-error-accept-inner
      h2.modal-error-accept-title Tittle error
      p.modal-error-accept-message
        | Contrary to&nbsp;popular belief, Lorem Ipsum is&nbsp;not simply random text. It&nbsp;has roots in&nbsp;a&nbsp;piece of&nbsp;classical Latin literature from 45&nbsp;BC, making it&nbsp;over 2000 years old. Richard McClintock, a&nbsp;Latin professor at&nbsp;Hampden-Sydney College in&nbsp;Virginia, looked up&nbsp;one of&nbsp;the more obscure
      .modal-error-accept-buttons
